{"title":"Docker 安装与升级","date":"2023-06-12T11:11:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 12, 2023","L":"06/12/2023","MM-DD":"06-12"},"link":"2023/06/12/Docker/01-Docker安装与升级","tags":["Docker"],"updated":"2023-06-12T11:19:38.441Z","content":"<h1 id=\"卸载旧版本\">卸载旧版本<a title=\"#卸载旧版本\" href=\"#卸载旧版本\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo yum remove docker \\<br>docker-client \\<br>docker-client-latest \\<br>docker-common \\<br>docker-latest \\<br>docker-latest-logrotate \\<br>docker-logrotate \\<br>docker-engine<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>/var/lib/docker/</code> 的内容，包括 image、container、volumes, and networks，将被保留。Docker 引擎包现在被称为 <code>docker-ce</code>。</p>\n<h1 id=\"设置存储库\">设置存储库<a title=\"#设置存储库\" href=\"#设置存储库\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo yum install -y yum-utils<br>sudo yum-config-manager \\<br>--add-repo \\<br>https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"安装-docker-引擎\">安装 Docker 引擎<a title=\"#安装-docker-引擎\" href=\"#安装-docker-引擎\"></a></h1>\n<p>查看版本列表:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">yum list docker-ce --showduplicates | <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sort</span> -r<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装最新版本的 Docker Engine 和 containerd:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo yum install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装指定版本的安装方式:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo yum install docker-ce-&lt;VERSION_STRING&gt; docker-ce-cli-&lt;VERSION_STRING&gt; containerd.io<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"启动-docker\">启动 Docker<a title=\"#启动-docker\" href=\"#启动-docker\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo systemctl start docker<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"Docker 安装 MySQL8 数据库","link":"2023/06/12/Docker/02-Docker安装MYSQL8数据库"},"next":{"title":"TienChin 开篇-运行 RuoYiVue","link":"2023/06/11/项目/TienChin 健身系统/2023-6-11/01-TienChin 开篇-运行 RuoYiVue"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/06/12/Docker/01-Docker安装与升级/","toc":[{"id":"卸载旧版本","title":"卸载旧版本","index":"1"},{"id":"设置存储库","title":"设置存储库","index":"2"},{"id":"安装-docker-引擎","title":"安装 Docker 引擎","index":"3"},{"id":"启动-docker","title":"启动 Docker","index":"4"}],"reading_time":"164 words in 1 min"}